{
  "texts": [
    "[48, 96, 140] proposed a drone-based prediction system that uses a network to identify patients with COVID-19.",
    "This model is implemented in areas with no Internet or wireless connections, and is used to identify and sanitize infected cases.",
    "[83, 93, 118] suggested using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) to detect COVID-19 using CT images.",
    "[36, 136] recommended using a combination of quantum and quantuminspired algorithms with deep learning, and introduced a development tool called DeepQUantum.",
    "This software was used to predict the variants of COVID-19 and has been shown to be more accurate than the regular hybrid and deep learning models."
  ]
}